{
  "texts": [
    "In the current Crop-GPA, of the 10,566 genes with at least one phenotype hit, 2964 showcased a distinctive gene-phenotype association by linking with multiple traits.",
    "Overall, Crop-GPA offers a comprehensive repository and two computational tools for the analysis and exploration of crop phenotypic studies.",
    "The platform provides a convenient way to gain a quick overall understanding of genes and traits, allowing users to intuitively access information about an entire genephenotype association data by a visual representation.",
    "Moving forward, we will continue to integrate new data from available resources and update our database regularly, mainly for gene and phenotype data from large-scale genomics projects.",
    "Our work addresses the crucial challenge of reusing a vast amount of literature data and leveraging it for prediction purposes."
  ]
}